org.sql: SELECT users.* FROM users WHERE LOWER(login) LIKE '%firstname%' OR LOWER(CONCAT(firstname, ' ', lastname)) LIKE '%firstname%' OR LOWER(CONCAT(lastname, ' ', firstname)) LIKE '%firstname%' OR LOWER(mail) LIKE '%firstname%' ORDER BY users.type ASC, users.login ASC, users.lastname ASC, users.firstname ASC, users.mail ASC
